{"tid":1953980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲首國！捷克宣布與台灣建立合作夥伴關係","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T18:00:09.000Z","uid":323443,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6c116f13ba92a24332ff9147a511da4df8c71ab9","tid":1953980,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"繼<span style=\"color: red;\">「台美防疫夥伴關係聯合聲明」</span>，捷克今（1）也與台灣簽署並共同發表<span style=\"color: red;\">「台捷抗疫合作聯合聲明」</span>。捷克科學院日前已與中研院洽談合作事宜，此聲明則是台灣與歐洲國家對抗武漢肺炎所簽署的第一個合作架構，展現台灣醫衛實力與貢獻國際期盼。<br />\n<br />\n我駐捷克代表柯良叡與捷克駐台代表Patrick Rumlar今天共同發表「台捷抗疫合作聯合聲明」。<br />\n<br />\n根據聲明內容，台灣與捷克雙方機構將協調並分享最佳實踐和合作，夥伴關係合作架構為多面向合作，包括：<br />\n<br />\n研發快篩檢驗試劑、<br />\n疫苗的研究與生產、<br />\n藥物的研究與生產、<br />\n醫療器械技術研究與轉讓、<br />\n案例旅遊史及後續追蹤、<br />\n交流最佳實踐和技術、<br />\n指定的訊息共享窗口、<br />\n醫療用品和設備的合作與交流。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3120418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3120418&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=c8e00d83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3120418&h=74add6cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3120418</a><br />\n<br />\n耿爽表示："},{"pid":"31e13ca5ceb2584538ee9455b6cab9185a27f5e3","tid":1953980,"uid":3513,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"WHO準備單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65e75d9b5a6bfbcea423dcc8fbf30bcc1080765","tid":1953980,"uid":24345,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"果然對抗過蘇共嘅國家都係有骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後如果去歐洲真係首選波蘭捷克東歐嗰邊"},{"pid":"dd5639c